snippet.title: TheCod3r
snippet.description:
Part time programmer, full time technician. If it's broken, I'll try and fix it. If it works, I'll try and break it.

Giving electronics a new lease on life is a great way to keep things out of the scrap heap and landfill, and if it's already broken there's no harm in trying the fix it.

Come along on my journey with me and learn how to fix stuff together.

Need a repair? Contact me via email at hello@consolefix.co.uk and I'll always get back to you.

Thanks for checking out my channel!
